{plot(data2[,2], resi1, main = '잔차 대 X1', xlab = 'X1', ylab ='잔차')
  abline(h=0, lty = 2)}

  abline(h=0, lty = 2)}

  abline(h=0, lty = 2)}

  abline(h=0, lty = 2)}
